reviewText: Arrive in excellent condition and fast. Very interesting,inspiring C.D. I wold recommend ti to people who want to see how Christ is working in other countries.

Ever wonder about if God is calling you into support worldwide mission work? This DVD is a great confirmation. Gospel for Asia is a fruitful mission group and K.p. does a fine job explaining the great commission!

This is a must see for anyone who wishes to follow Jesus Christ...  It will really help you find the narrow path!  This video was a HUGE blessing to me and really helped me.

God Bless,

Jonathan
